race.description: Xxxx Ginger Beer Country Stampede Qualifier Hcp
race.comment: INVAHIR (4) was well supported when resuming last start but missed the placings in fifth over 1000m at Gayndah. Second-up record is strong. Has the pace to settle in the leading division and best figures should see him run well. FLANK SPEED (3) was well in commission last time but ran below expectations when fourth and beaten 6 lengths over 1200m at Charleville. Has a strong record at this course, scoring three times from four starts and rates among the leading chances. SMILING ZAC (6) is on a 7 day turnaround after placing at Chinchilla last time out. Has had great success when backed up quickly having won two races that way. Should be poised just off the lead and will give backers a sight. ABLETT (11) finished 2.5 lengths away from the winner last time at Moree and drops in the weights. Don't underestimate.
